{"type":"answer","id":2486,"parentType":"question","parentId":562,"uid":1015,"contents":"永远的红太阳，伟大的时代舵手，<br>\n<br>\n一句话:谁敢批判毛主席，我就砸烂谁的狗头。<br>\n<br>\n不得不说他的权术非常厉害，包括早期的王明，张国焘等还是建国后刘少奇，彭德怀等都不是他的对手。<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180501/e002e0e544301b5e395fabd9a355892c.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180501/e002e0e544301b5e395fabd9a355892c.jpeg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180501/e002e0e544301b5e395fabd9a355892c.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-02","agreeCount":12,"discussionCount":4}